Shaoqing.

4
00:01:20,690 --> 00:01:22,250
Sorry, am I late?

5
00:01:24,450 --> 00:01:25,290
Not at all.

6
00:01:25,450 --> 00:01:26,290
You're right on time.

7
00:01:27,690 --> 00:01:30,090
Did you pick out this outfit yourself today?

8
00:01:32,010 --> 00:01:34,010
It's elegant and suits you perfectly.

9
00:01:34,730 --> 00:01:36,450
I remember you said

10
00:01:36,850 --> 00:01:38,570
that you want to create

11
00:01:38,570 --> 00:01:41,690
a private haute couture brand named Xiluo.

12
00:01:41,850 --> 00:01:42,690
Still interested?

13
00:01:42,690 --> 00:01:44,770
- What's private haute couture?
- I'll invest in you.

14
00:01:45,210 --> 00:01:47,090
You wouldn't understand high society matters.

15
00:01:47,090 --> 00:01:49,410
Not interested for now.

16
00:01:49,530 --> 00:01:50,890
Let's talk when there's a chance.

17
00:01:51,130 --> 00:01:51,970
Alright.

18
00:01:52,290 --> 00:01:53,370
Then let's head inside.

19
00:01:53,570 --> 00:01:55,250
Let's go.

20
00:02:06,810 --> 00:02:08,450
I need to go in and work for Ms. Su.

21
00:02:08,570 --> 00:02:10,090
I'm her personal assistant.

22
00:02:10,210 --> 00:02:11,410
Personal assistant, huh?

23
00:02:11,970 --> 00:02:13,410
Assistants can only wait outside.

24
00:02:21,670 --> 00:02:22,610
Personal assistant, huh?

25
00:02:22,610 --> 00:02:24,330
Assistants can only wait outside.

26
00:02:43,770 --> 00:02:44,770
From Luoshen Group?

27
00:02:46,810 --> 00:02:48,330
How... How do you know?

28
00:02:48,730 --> 00:02:49,890
I've read your profile.

29
00:02:50,770 --> 00:02:51,770
Zhao Chuxi, right?

30
00:02:52,850 --> 00:02:53,690
Yes.

31
00:02:53,850 --> 00:02:54,850
My name is Zhao Chuxi.

32
00:02:55,170 --> 00:02:57,130
I'm Ms. Su's driver at Luoshen Group.

33
00:02:57,370 --> 00:02:58,770
If I'm not mistaken,

34
00:02:59,770 --> 00:03:01,170
you and Xu Shaoqing don't get along.

35
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,990
There's hostility between you two.

36
00:03:03,050 --> 00:03:04,090
His hostility toward you

37
00:03:04,090 --> 00:03:05,770
is because you're too close to Su Xiluo.

38
00:03:06,330 --> 00:03:07,510
And your hostility toward him,

39
00:03:07,690 --> 00:03:08,530
first,

40
00:03:09,090 --> 00:03:10,530
you just can't stand his attitude;

41
00:03:11,050 --> 00:03:11,890
second,

42
00:03:13,130 --> 00:03:14,490
it's also because of Su Xiluo.

43
00:03:18,570 --> 00:03:20,450
Don't you think this woman is a bit sly?

44
00:03:21,010 --> 00:03:22,210
Using you as a pawn.

45
00:03:23,890 --> 00:03:25,130
With your current strength,

46
00:03:25,130 --> 00:03:26,850
what benefit is there

47
00:03:28,130 --> 00:03:29,210
in opposing Xu Shaoqing?

48
00:03:33,650 --> 00:03:35,570
You're here to gather intel, aren't you?

49
00:03:38,170 --> 00:03:39,010
Smart.

50
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:42,250
Let me ask you one question.

51
00:03:42,250 --> 00:03:43,250
Make your choice.

52
00:03:44,730 --> 00:03:46,650
If I told you to stay neutral,

53
00:03:47,810 --> 00:03:49,490
to advance or withdraw,

54
00:03:49,970 --> 00:03:51,730
holding onto Su Xiluo tightly,

55
00:03:52,330 --> 00:03:54,010
or distancing yourself from her,

56
00:03:55,410 --> 00:03:56,290
what would you choose?

57
00:03:58,930 --> 00:04:00,250
Do I have to answer?

58
00:04:00,610 --> 00:04:01,850
If I tell you,

59
00:04:01,970 --> 00:04:02,970
your answer will decide

60
00:04:02,970 --> 00:04:05,130
whether the cooperation is successful.

61
00:04:05,930 --> 00:04:06,770
Dare to bet?

62
00:04:15,610 --> 00:04:16,690
I don't dare.

63
00:04:16,690 --> 00:04:17,890
I don't have the leverage.

64
00:04:18,410 --> 00:04:19,370
But,

65
00:04:19,610 --> 00:04:21,810
I must tightly hold onto Su Xiluo.

66
00:04:22,010 --> 00:04:23,330
She's my stepping stone.

67
00:04:23,330 --> 00:04:24,530
If I leave her,

68
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:26,190
I'll definitely fall back to square one.

69
00:04:30,970 --> 00:04:31,810
Smart,

70
00:04:32,690 --> 00:04:34,290
bold, and ambitious.

71
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,050
But let me tell you this,

72
00:04:38,050 --> 00:04:39,770
it's good for a man to have ambition.

73
00:04:40,570 --> 00:04:42,030
But you must learn to keep it hidden.

74
00:04:42,140 --> 00:04:43,550
Being too rigid can lead to failure.

75
00:04:44,770 --> 00:04:46,930
I understand your desire

76
00:04:47,610 --> 00:04:48,490
to rise above.

77
00:04:51,210 --> 00:04:52,610
I fear poverty.

78
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:53,570
I lack money.

79
00:04:57,890 --> 00:04:59,250
Let me introduce myself.

80
00:04:59,250 --> 00:05:00,170
My name is Xu Lin.

81
00:05:01,410 --> 00:05:02,690
You really match my vibe.

82
00:05:03,850 --> 00:05:05,010
Would you like to be friends?

83
00:05:05,810 --> 00:05:06,650
Sure.

84
00:05:06,730 --> 00:05:07,570
Absolutely.

85
00:05:14,490 --> 00:05:15,490
Xu, this...

86
00:05:16,170 --> 00:05:17,130
This scene...

87
00:05:17,850 --> 00:05:19,770
This is so-called high society, huh?

88
00:05:23,210 --> 00:05:24,370
This is life.

89
00:05:25,690 --> 00:05:27,170
Life is full of pretenses everywhere.

90
00:05:27,410 --> 00:05:28,850
That's why so many people

91
00:05:28,850 --> 00:05:30,770
will do anything to enter high society.

92
00:05:31,050 --> 00:05:32,610
Those with no money or little money,

93
00:05:32,850 --> 00:05:34,010
come here to make a living.

94
00:05:34,010 --> 00:05:35,290
As for the wealthy ones,

95
00:05:35,730 --> 00:05:37,650
they come here to prove their worth.

96
00:05:39,810 --> 00:05:41,010
Remember this:

97
00:05:41,770 --> 00:05:44,050
shallow waters, plenty of wannabes.

98
00:05:44,490 --> 00:05:46,170
You'll only know,

99
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,410
who's swimming naked when the tide recedes.

100
00:05:49,090 --> 00:05:49,970
Xu,

101
00:05:50,730 --> 00:05:52,370
you must have seen a lot

102
00:05:53,050 --> 00:05:55,330
to say that, huh?

103
00:05:56,010 --> 00:05:58,610
How about I work with you?

104
00:05:59,090 --> 00:06:01,130
(This guy is so shameless)

105
00:06:01,570 --> 00:06:03,610
(that reminds me of my younger self.)

106
00:06:07,650 --> 00:06:09,010
Get your footing first.

107
00:06:09,570 --> 00:06:11,370
Then we'll talk when you're stronger.

108
00:06:14,370 --> 00:06:17,050
At first, they were still on the fence.

109
00:06:17,290 --> 00:06:18,890
But after your negotiation,

110
00:06:19,850 --> 00:06:21,410
they're scrambling to invest in you

111
00:06:21,410 --> 00:06:22,570
and afraid you'd run away.

112
00:06:23,170 --> 00:06:25,930
Xiluo, you always manage to give me

113
00:06:26,450 --> 00:06:27,930
unexpected surprises.

114
00:06:28,170 --> 00:06:29,130
Not really.

115
00:06:29,130 --> 00:06:29,970
Of course,

116
00:06:30,810 --> 00:06:34,930
sometimes, there are tiny shocks too.

117
00:06:35,330 --> 00:06:36,210
Like

118
00:06:37,370 --> 00:06:38,210
that person.

119
00:06:43,330 --> 00:06:44,610
Didn't you promise me

120
00:06:44,850 --> 00:06:46,530
not to let him be your assistant anymore?

121
00:06:47,850 --> 00:06:49,410
I almost forgot about this.

122
00:06:49,570 --> 00:06:52,730
Shaoqing, I think you're absolutely right.

123
00:06:52,730 --> 00:06:55,250
He's not suited to be an assistant.

124
00:06:55,570 --> 00:06:56,690
So now,

125
00:06:56,690 --> 00:06:58,570
he's my driver and bodyguard.

126
00:07:12,570 --> 00:07:15,690
Fancy wine parties? Not even filling.

127
00:07:16,970 --> 00:07:18,090
Driver and bodyguard,

128
00:07:18,290 --> 00:07:19,690
you're still not full?

129
00:07:20,010 --> 00:07:21,370
That's all what you've got.

130
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,810
How does me eating a sausage bother you?

131
00:07:23,810 --> 00:07:25,410
Talking all day long.

132
00:07:25,410 --> 00:07:26,250
Zhao Chuxi,

133
00:07:26,530 --> 00:07:27,610
you made a new friend?

134
00:07:28,290 --> 00:07:30,650
I just met a guy, and he's quite interesting.

135
00:07:30,650 --> 00:07:31,690
Quite interesting?

136
00:07:32,570 --> 00:07:34,490
You know, he's not as simple as he seems.

137
00:07:34,490 --> 00:07:37,290
He's officially an assistant at his company,

138
00:07:37,290 --> 00:07:39,690
but he's actually the one

139
00:07:39,690 --> 00:07:40,810
making all the decisions.

140
00:07:42,530 --> 00:07:43,370
Zhao Chuxi,

141
00:07:43,530 --> 00:07:45,450
if you can become friends with him,

142
00:07:45,860 --> 00:07:47,010
I'll owe you big time.

143
00:07:47,290 --> 00:07:48,850
Alright, I got it.

144
00:07:49,290 --> 00:07:50,170
Alright?

145
00:07:51,290 --> 00:07:52,930
Alright, Fusheng BBQ.

146
00:07:53,050 --> 00:07:53,890
Let's go!

147
00:07:58,490 --> 00:07:59,610
Driver and bodyguard,

148
00:07:59,610 --> 00:08:00,850
you just got your license.

149
00:08:00,850 --> 00:08:02,490
It's time to test your skills.

150
00:08:02,490 --> 00:08:04,930
Just don't press the brake and gas together!

151
00:08:05,130 --> 00:08:06,730
You're always so talkative all day.

152
00:08:06,730 --> 00:08:08,530
My driving skills are top-notch now.

153
00:08:13,570 --> 00:08:14,610
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

154
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:23,470
I have a few words to say.

155
00:08:24,330 --> 00:08:25,170
First of all,

156
00:08:25,410 --> 00:08:26,250
Lu Yao,

157
00:08:26,730 --> 00:08:27,650
I want to thank you.

158
00:08:28,490 --> 00:08:29,450
Because of you,

159
00:08:30,770 --> 00:08:32,930
I found the courage to face my heart.

160
00:08:33,330 --> 00:08:34,450
Absolutely right.

161
00:08:34,850 --> 00:08:36,890
Also, without her, you wouldn't drive.

162
00:08:36,890 --> 00:08:37,810
- Exactly.
- Yeah.

163
00:08:38,410 --> 00:08:39,490
- Yeah.
- And also,

164
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:41,410
I need to thank you, Chuxi.

165
00:08:41,930 --> 00:08:43,650
Ms. Su, no need to be so formal with me.

166
00:08:43,650 --> 00:08:44,890
Thank you for coming back.

167
00:08:45,930 --> 00:08:47,490
Come on, cheers.

168
00:08:47,490 --> 00:08:48,330
Here we go.

169
00:08:50,210 --> 00:08:51,210
Cheers!

170
00:08:51,210 --> 00:08:52,090
Just go!

171
00:09:00,210 --> 00:09:01,050
Ms. Su,

172
00:09:02,570 --> 00:09:04,010
I've always admired you.

173
00:09:04,010 --> 00:09:04,850
Why?

174
00:09:05,090 --> 00:09:05,930
You know,

175
00:09:06,530 --> 00:09:08,250
you're the one in this world,

176
00:09:09,730 --> 00:09:11,130
aside from my sister,

177
00:09:11,810 --> 00:09:13,210
that I admire the most.

178
00:09:13,210 --> 00:09:14,050
Wait a second.

179
00:09:14,450 --> 00:09:15,810
You have a sister?

180
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:17,850
She's my adoptive father's daughter.

181
00:09:18,770 --> 00:09:20,930
Is your sister pretty?

182
00:09:20,930 --> 00:09:22,370
Much prettier than you.

183
00:09:22,890 --> 00:09:23,730
You...

184
00:09:24,450 --> 00:09:25,370
Me what?

185
00:09:27,130 --> 00:09:28,890
Is your sister prettier,

186
00:09:28,890 --> 00:09:30,890
or is Ms. Su prettier?

187
00:09:33,010 --> 00:09:34,170
Each has their charm.

188
00:09:35,170 --> 00:09:36,290
Wrong answer.

189
00:09:36,290 --> 00:09:37,610
- Punish you.
- Punish you!

190
00:09:38,650 --> 00:09:39,490
Go ahead.

191
00:09:41,090 --> 00:09:41,970
Zhao Chuxi,

192
00:09:42,530 --> 00:09:43,970
you're a good person

193
00:09:43,970 --> 00:09:45,410
in every way,

194
00:09:45,530 --> 00:09:46,650
but you have one shortcoming

195
00:09:47,050 --> 00:09:48,210
that you're too honest.

196
00:09:48,690 --> 00:09:49,530
Drink up!

197
00:09:50,370 --> 00:09:51,330
Is being honest bad?

198
00:09:51,330 --> 00:09:52,170
Just drink!

199
00:09:52,180 --> 00:09:53,890
People in the village are all honest.

200
00:09:54,810 --> 00:09:56,930
- Come on!
- You're really good at it.

201
00:09:57,290 --> 00:09:58,370
I respond really fast.

202
00:09:58,370 --> 00:09:59,330
Faster than you.

203
00:10:00,170 --> 00:10:01,010
Cheers.

204
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:19,900
(Shui She Suite Hotel)

205
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:25,370
Can you walk by yourself?

206
00:10:26,690 --> 00:10:27,530
I...

207
00:10:27,650 --> 00:10:28,490
I can't.

208
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:32,570
My legs feel weak. I can't move.

209
00:10:33,010 --> 00:10:34,030
Let me help you. Come on.

210
00:10:38,050 --> 00:10:38,930
Take it slow, okay?

211
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:40,510
Oh dear, you're quite heavy.

212
00:10:49,850 --> 00:10:50,810
Ms. Su,

213
00:10:51,210 --> 00:10:52,130
is this your friend?

214
00:10:52,370 --> 00:10:53,210
Yes.

215
00:10:53,290 --> 00:10:54,690
Why did he drink so much?

216
00:10:54,690 --> 00:10:55,690
Come on, let me help you.

217
00:10:56,530 --> 00:10:57,370
No need.

218
00:10:57,530 --> 00:10:58,370
It's fine.

219
00:10:58,370 --> 00:10:59,410
Don't be polite, buddy.

220
00:10:59,410 --> 00:11:01,290
We security guards are really professional.

221
00:11:01,290 --> 00:11:03,290
- Come on.
- I don't need you.

222
00:11:03,290 --> 00:11:04,490
I've got Ms. Su.

223
00:11:04,490 --> 00:11:06,050
Ms. Su is just a young lady.

224
00:11:06,050 --> 00:11:07,570
Look, you've already overwhelmed her.

225
00:11:07,570 --> 00:11:08,520
No need to be so formal.

226
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:09,890
It's... it's fine.

227
00:11:11,090 --> 00:11:12,410
Come on, buddy.

228
00:11:12,730 --> 00:11:13,690
Ms. Su, you go ahead.

229
00:11:13,970 --> 00:11:15,250
Alright.

230
00:11:16,290 --> 00:11:17,730
- I'll get the door.
- Alright then.

231
00:11:18,650 --> 00:11:19,490
Your arm...

232
00:11:19,930 --> 00:11:21,090
Arm... Let's go.

233
00:11:23,850 --> 00:11:25,730
Why are you so clueless?

234
00:11:25,730 --> 00:11:27,930
Can't you figure this out?

235
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:29,730
People never ruin a marriage.

236
00:11:29,730 --> 00:11:31,170
Don't mess up my plans.

237
00:11:32,650 --> 00:11:33,650
Ms. Su.

238
00:11:35,330 --> 00:11:36,170
Ms. Su.

239
00:11:40,130 --> 00:11:43,490
Did I ruin a marriage?

240
00:11:45,530 --> 00:11:47,530
This city is indeed full of tricks.

241
00:12:01,970 --> 00:12:03,370
Such a deep scar.

242
00:12:05,370 --> 00:12:06,770
That must've hurt a lot.

243
00:12:29,570 --> 00:12:31,530
What are you doing here?

244
00:12:33,210 --> 00:12:34,050
Nothing.

245
00:12:34,370 --> 00:12:36,130
Don't get me wrong.

246
00:12:36,850 --> 00:12:38,650
I bring my brother to you. This is my robe.

247
00:12:40,450 --> 00:12:41,290
No.

248
00:12:41,370 --> 00:12:43,650
My brother asked me to bring you a robe.

249
00:12:44,410 --> 00:12:45,290
Your brother?

250
00:12:45,570 --> 00:12:46,530
It's not that.

251
00:12:46,850 --> 00:12:48,290
This is my brother's robe.

252
00:12:48,290 --> 00:12:49,810
I... I bring it to you.

253
00:12:54,690 --> 00:12:56,090
You get changed first, alright?

254
00:13:09,210 --> 00:13:10,650
Ms. Su,

255
00:13:10,650 --> 00:13:12,330
you always keep such a stern face,

256
00:13:12,930 --> 00:13:14,130
isn't that uncomfortable?

257
00:13:14,850 --> 00:13:16,250
You should smile more.

258
00:13:17,930 --> 00:13:20,170
Smiling makes the world a better place.

259
00:13:24,210 --> 00:13:25,690
I'll go prepare your bed.

260
00:13:29,090 --> 00:13:30,790
The sheets and covers have all been changed.

261
00:13:30,890 --> 00:13:31,810
They're clean.

262
00:13:32,130 --> 00:13:33,170
Rest easy and sleep well.

263
00:13:33,170 --> 00:13:34,650
Call me if you need anything.

264
00:13:35,010 --> 00:13:36,330
Or just send me a message.

265
00:13:45,770 --> 00:13:46,650
Go to bed early.

266
00:14:04,050 --> 00:14:05,450
Go to bed early.

267
00:14:42,370 --> 00:14:43,570
Why aren't you asleep yet?

268
00:14:46,410 --> 00:14:47,810
You're not sleeping either.

269
00:14:55,650 --> 00:14:56,610
What are you looking at?

270
00:14:57,370 --> 00:14:58,330
You look so good.

271
00:15:03,490 --> 00:15:04,410
Do I look good?

272
00:15:06,850 --> 00:15:07,690
Great.

273
00:15:07,890 --> 00:15:08,810
Do you like me?

274
00:15:11,090 --> 00:15:12,530
Who wouldn't like you?

275
00:15:25,450 --> 00:15:26,450
You dress like this.

276
00:15:27,130 --> 00:15:28,210
Aren't you afraid I might

277
00:15:28,490 --> 00:15:30,210
take things further?

278
00:15:43,050 --> 00:15:44,650
You're playing with fire here.

279
00:15:48,330 --> 00:15:49,890
Where's my room?

280
00:15:51,370 --> 00:15:52,210
Over there.

281
00:15:52,530 --> 00:15:54,090
I'm tired, going to sleep.

282
00:16:04,570 --> 00:16:05,970
Playing with fire?

283
00:16:08,290 --> 00:16:10,010
He got the desire but not the guts, huh?

284
00:16:26,330 --> 00:16:27,370
Come here, come here.

285
00:16:31,330 --> 00:16:32,290
What are you hiding for?

286
00:16:32,290 --> 00:16:33,170
Hey.

287
00:16:34,530 --> 00:16:36,010
I'm awkward to face you.

288
00:16:36,010 --> 00:16:37,810
I almost ruined your big moment last night.

