661
00:34:25,456 --> 00:34:30,756
♪I'm struggling for an ordinary script♪

662
00:34:32,186 --> 00:34:36,276
♪Despite the twists and turns,
it's just to survive♪

663
00:34:39,066 --> 00:34:43,616
♪I'm the one who left the small town♪

664
00:34:46,106 --> 00:34:50,916
♪The one who ate
while crying or laughing♪

665
00:34:53,646 --> 00:34:59,616
♪The one on the road,
